T - - the object this a vector of

V4 - - the object to return for this-returning methods

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface Vec4<T,V2 extends Vec2<T,V2>,V3 extends Vec3<T,V2,V3>,V4 extends Vec4<T,V2,V3,V4>> extends Vec3<T,V2,V3>
Utility class for vectors of any object. NOT INTENDED FOR USE AS GENERIC OBJECT VECTOR, USE Obj3
